  "contentHtml": "<html>\n<head>\n\t<title></title>\n\t<link href=\"https://simbli.eboardsolutions.com/ckeditor/plugins/lance/css/annotate.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n\t<link href=\"https://svc.webspellchecker.net/spellcheck31/lf/scayt3/ckscayt/css/wsc.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n\t<link href=\"/ckeditor/plugins/lite/css/lite.css?n=1234671010\" id=\"__lite__css__\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n\t<link href=\"https://simbli.eboardsolutions.com/ckeditor/plugins/lite/css/opentip.css\" id=\"__lite_tt_css__\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n\t<link href=\"https://simbli.eboardsolutions.com/ckeditor/plugins/lance/css/annotate.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n\t<link href=\"https://svc.webspellchecker.net/spellcheck31/wscbundle/css/wsc.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n</head>\n\n<body data-gramm_editor=\"false\" data-wsc-instance=\"true\">\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:transparent; border-collapse:inherit; border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:#000000; font-family:Lato; font-size:15px; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; line-height:normal; margin-bottom:1em; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:1em; orphans:2; outline:0px; padding:0px; text-align:left; text-decoration-color:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px\">Homeless students living in the district shall be admitted to district schools upon presentation of any of the following:</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: inherit; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; margin: 1em 0px; orphans: 2; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;\">Hotel or motel receipts</li>\n\t<li style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: inherit; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; margin: 1em 0px; orphans: 2; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;\">A letter from a social service agency or homeless shelter verifying that the student lives within the district</li>\n\t<li style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: inherit; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; margin: 1em 0px; orphans: 2; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;\">An affidavit from the parent/guardian stating that the family lives within the district</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:transparent; border-collapse:inherit; border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:#000000; font-family:Lato; font-size:15px; font-style:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; line-height:normal; margin-bottom:1em; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:1em; orphans:2; outline:0px; padding:0px; text-align:left; text-decoration-color:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px\">A reasonable effort shall be made to secure an address, phone number and medical release from the parent/guardian when a student is placed in a classroom.</p>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
  "contentText": "Homeless students living in the district shall be admitted to district schools upon presentation of any of the following:\n\n\tHotel or motel receipts\n\tA letter from a social service agency or homeless shelter verifying that the student lives within the district\n\tAn affidavit from the parent/guardian stating that the family lives within the district\n\nA reasonable effort shall be made to secure an address, phone number and medical release from the parent/guardian when a student is placed in a classroom.",
